  <Name>Cloud of Daggers</Name>
  <CastingTime>1 action</CastingTime>
  <Range>60 feet</Range>
  <Duration>Concentration, up to 1 minute</Duration>
  <Level>2</Level>
  <Description>You fill the air with spinning daggers in a cube 5 feet on each side, centered on a point you choose within range. A creature takes 4d4 slashing damage when it enters the spell's area for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there.</Description>
  <Descriptions>
    <Description>
      <Name>At Higher Levels</Name>
      <Text>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 2d4 for each slot level above 2nd.</Text>
    </Description>
  </Descriptions>
  <Source>Player's Handbook</Source>
